Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: Sort of pointlessly contrarian to disagree with this. But consider: - Lay people feel so free to opine on health/law that "your google search isn't equal to my degree" is a meme. - "I could not do that" is a common sentiment I hear when I tell people I program.
